Transmutation
Level: Drd 9
Components: V, S
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Short
Target: Personal
Duration: 1 round/level
Saving Throw: Will negates
Spell Resistance: Yes

Anyone meeting your gaze is permanently turned into a mindless, inert status ( as Flesh To Stone ).

Each round a gaze attack automatically works against one random creature within range that is looking at ( attacking or interacting with ) the gazing creature.